snippet.title: Barbie: Gotta Have Games [20] PS1 Longplay
snippet.description:
Barbie: Gotta Have Games is a 2003 party game where you can visit 8 different locations to play a minigame. Each minigame is a reimagined form of classic games such as going to the arcade for hangman or the ice cream shop for connect 4.

#ps1 #barbie #retrogaming
